        <title>ECONOMY MODE SWITCH</title>
        <para>The shift selector has an ECONOMY MODE SWITCH (
            <hotlnk document="s08247_6.xml" xrefid="f0824703">Figure 3</hotlnk>). The switch is used to select
            transmission shift schedules for economy or performance. The switch will be lighted when "Economy Mode" is
            selected.
        </para>
